         <p id="BUpLJr" outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(3) Actions that do not require an AP:</p>
         <p id="GnNWis" outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(a) Task/delivery orders issued in accordance with the terms of the basic contract except non-DoD orders;</p>
         <p id="VqhLkd" outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(b) Modifications within the scope of the contract;</p>
         <p id="pLNDtF" outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(c) Replenishment parts except for those replenishment buys that require design; development, verification testing, and approval before start of production and</p>
